Stderr: 0.43205607882642
clear # Clear any previous runs
  using 8 OpenMP thread(s) per MPI task

package omp 8 # For parallelisation.
using multi-threaded neighbor list subroutines


### DEFINE SIMULATION BOX GEOMETRY ###
lattice sc 0.8
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 1.0772173 1.0772173 1.0772173
region box block 0 5 0 5 0 5
create_box 1 box
Created orthogonal box = (0.0000000 0.0000000 0.0000000) to (5.3860867 5.3860867 5.3860867)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
create_atoms 1 box
Created 125 atoms
  create_atoms CPU = 0.001 seconds

### DEFINE PHYSICAL PROPERTIES OF ATOMS ###
mass 1 1.0
pair_style lj/cut/omp 2.5
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0
neighbor 2.0 bin

### SPECIFY THE REQUIRED THERMODYNAMIC STATE ###
variable T equal 2.25
variable p equal 3
variable timestep equal 0.001

log ${T}_${p}_NpT.log # specify the log file name. Can overwrite if desired
log 2.25_${p}_NpT.log 
log 2.25_3_NpT.log 
